 then I urge you to register right now.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong><a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/PracticeTest.asp">That sounds great I&rsquo;d like to take the free test Now!</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><br />\nRemember there are unlimited FREE tests and loads of FREE tutorial typing games and learning materials available so you can&nbsp;<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/ImproveYourSpeed.asp" target="_blank">improve your typing skills</a>&nbsp;quickly and easily in a fun and exciting way before you even pay one cent! And your certificate is completely&hellip;Guaranteed!<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#ff0000">Why settle for anything less than a truly rewarding life?</span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><br />\nWith great typing and keyboarding skills the world can be your oyster&hellip;and you&rsquo;ll have your cake and eat it too.<br />\n<br />\nAnd what&rsquo;s better, the change and development is fast and for a lifetime&hellip;with only a little effort on your behalf.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">There&rsquo;s absolutely no reason why you should keep struggling and suffering the disappointment of missing out on employment.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nYou know there is so much more to this life of yours. While you linger without improving your abilities you&rsquo;re only &ldquo;half living&rdquo; and you&rsquo;re missing out on all the good things that should be yours.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;You don&rsquo;t have to go on banging your head against a brick wall and missing out on work opportunities because you can&rsquo;t type with the efficiency you desire.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;If you don&rsquo;t make a stand right now nothing, absolutely nothing will change.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nIf everything were sweet and rosy in your life and money poured in out of nowhere you wouldn&rsquo;t be reading this letter. So you have taken the first step&hellip;and first step is awareness.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;You&rsquo;ve acknowledged that you need to improve your keyboarding and typing skills to get work and I admire you for your courage.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#ff0000">The next step is action&hellip;</span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong><a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/PracticeTest.asp">I agree please test me right now!</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;Whatever it is that you want, whether you want a promotion or a new job to bring in regular income that&rsquo;s been missing in your life&hellip;you will greatly improve your opportunities and horizons&hellip;with my unique typing and keyboarding skills and development online site.<br />\n<br />\nBecome the person you want to be!<br />\n<br />\nExperience the thrill of actually getting your typing skills up to speed and accuracy and landing that new job or promotion because you&rsquo;ve impressed your employer. The rewards are waiting for you.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nI look forward to you joining me and so many of my satisfied members at TypingCertification.com.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWarm Regards,</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="http://www.typingcertification.com/UserFiles/Image/signature(.png" style="height:50px; width:222px" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nP.S. Remember your Typing Certificate is full guaranteed, so if for some unusual reason an employer does not accept it you don&rsquo;t risk one cent. That&rsquo;s how confident I am that you&rsquo;ll be happy with your results.<br />\n<br />\nP.P.S. And please don&rsquo;s forget my FREE LIMITED TIME eBOOK OFFER: For this month only, buy 4 tests at the incredibly low price of $12.95 and get the &ldquo;10 Insider Secrets to Job Hunting Success &ndash; Everything You Need to Get the Job in 24 Hours or Less&rdquo; Valued at $19.95!<br />\n<br />\nP.P.P.S. For&nbsp;<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/CorporateRegistration.asp">corporate users</a>&nbsp;please usually order&nbsp; in multiples of our FOUR tests for $13.95 , you only pay $3.48 each to remote test your candidates.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">However this month, just sign up and email us for 5 FREE credits to test our system!</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>'),
(2, 'About US', 'About Us', 'Yes', '<p>TypingCertification.com, was established by Language Direct, a company that brings challenging, interesting and useful tools to the Internet. The integrity of this site is paramount. Tests are designed to duplicate real-life testing experiences. Further, the integrity of the site is not diluted with advertising or other distractions. The site pays for itself with minimal fees collected from test takers. While the fees are low enough to be affordable to all, charging fees reinforces our commitment to making sure that every test is worth something to the test taker. Each one of the tests on the site offers a true and valuable opportunity to show what you know. A printed certificate lets the holder display their level of expertise to friends, parents, teachers and employers. If you would like to know more about TypingCertification.com, please email</p>\r\n\r\n<p>webmaster@TypingCertification.com<br />\r\nLanguage Direct<br />\r\nNumber 1963<br />\r\n14781 Memorial Dr.<br />\r\nHouston, TX 77079<br />\r\nUSA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other related Language Direct sites are .....</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.certificatecenter.com/" target="_blank">Certificate Center Online Testing Certification</a><br />\r\nEmployee Testing Tutorials - Corporate Training</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.phuketvacationapartments.com/">Phuket Holiday Apartments</a><br />\r\nBest place for a holiday in Asia!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.teststeststests.com/" target="_blank">Tests Tests Tests</a><br />\r\nRanging from serious IQ tests to the Sexual Color Test!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.languagedirect.com/" target="_blank">Language Direct Study Languages&nbsp;</a><br />\r\nBest Language Learning Site Online&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>'),
(3, NULL, 'Corporate Registration', 'Yes', '<p>This registration form is only for corporate users who would be using our site to test others. In case you are not a corporate user, please<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/Includes/FCKeditor/editor/Register.asp">click here</a>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease enter your full name, company name, email address and password in the form below and click on the &quot;Register&quot; button once.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAfter registration of a corporate account, and payment for a number of tests. You will be able to send each candidate an email with their unique login details to take the test, and you will be informed of the results immediately after the test is taken.<br />\r\nBoth you and the candidate will also be able to print an official certificate showing the results if desired.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n=========<br />\r\n&quot;Yes, that&#39;s what I needed.&nbsp; Thanks!&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I used most of the credits today.<br />\r\nThanks for offering a great site that meets our needs.&quot;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLinda Higbee<br />\r\nAdministrative Assistant<br />\r\nTipton County Extension Education Center<br />\r\n=========<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeel free to open an account and then email me for&nbsp;FIVE free creditsto test our system. (special, this month only)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCheers,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://www.universityoflife.com/UserFiles/Image/Picture%201%281%29.png" style="height:50px; width:222px" /></p>'),
(4, NULL, 'FAQ', 'Yes', '<p>FAQ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTE: There is only one space after a period, as per&nbsp;<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/ArticleView.asp?ArticleID=11" target="_blank">How many spaces after a period when typing?</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(1)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ)&nbsp;<br />\r\nI am Kenneth Todd and my comments are : I just have a question for you.<br />\r\nI am thinking about taking the cerified test around Monday night before a job interview on Tuesday. My question to you is, if I did the typing certificate thing and if the employer was to not accept this certificate, then how do we go about getting my money back if that was to happen. Do I have to have them fill out a form or something. I am sure that there would be some way that I would have to prove that, this happened to me. I am not saying that it would but I am just trying to cover myself too. I would hate to lose out on being able to get a refund if this happened because I did not take the proper steps to cover myself too. I would appreciate a response on this. Thank you very much.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA)&nbsp;<br />\r\nHi Kenneth, yes, you would just contact me (with user name and if you paid with PayPal or 2CO) and let me know name of company and phone number. We immediately refund your money. Then later and anonymously, we contact them and find out their typing test policy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n===============<br />\r\n(2)<br />\r\nQ)<br />\r\nI am Satinder and my comments are : i have question. i need to take typing test but below are the requirements that i need to have on certificate. do you guys have this.<br />\r\ncertificate or signed statement needs to include below<br />\r\nQ1). That i took 5 mins typing test<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA1)<br />\r\nYou can choose a 5 min test.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ2).My score in gross speed,number of error,and net speed<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA2) Yes, all included...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ3). Date of exam<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA3) Included<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ4) Signature of staff veryfying the results of exam<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA4) All certificates are signed by IE Hewitt as Auditor and M Sharp as Analyst<br />\r\n<br />\r\n==============<br />\r\n(3)<br />\r\nQ)<br />\r\nI am Sherry Kluxdal and my comments are : Hello,<br />\r\nI have a question ... Why would an employer accept a printed certificate from a test generated on your site when it would be simple enough to have someone with better typing skills take the test for the applicant?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA)<br />\r\nIf you are dishonest enough and find another as dishonest as that, then you could cheat, but what good would that do if you got the job? You would be found out eventually, so no point.&nbsp;<br />\r\nAlso, like other online certification, we feel the use of credit card (that matches the test takers name) as pretty reasonable proof that it is the credit card owner who took the test.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n=================<br />\r\n(4)<br />\r\nQ)<br />\r\nWhat are the subjects of the tests and can I choose which I get?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA)<br />\r\nThe tests are chosen at random so there is a variety and are not likely to be memorized. The sujects are as follows...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBusiness Plan<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEarth History<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHarry Potter&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMystery&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlanet Pluto&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPolitics&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSherlock Holmes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5)<br />\r\nQ)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi. I was just wondering if your certificate is recognizable up in Canada?&nbsp;<br />\r\nI need to have a typing certification for the Royal Canadian Mounted&nbsp;<br />\r\nPolice and was not wanting to have to hit up a college.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A)<br />\r\nHmm, you need to ask them really. The police always want a 5 min test which we do. But they sometimes insist on the test being &quot;supervised&quot; which means someone watches the test, which we don&#39;t provide.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou may suggest that you do the test in their office while they watch.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Q)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi, should I use one space or two after a period?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These days it is accepted that just one space is used after a period.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>===================</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi Darren,&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIs your typing certificate / test created using Mavis Beacon software?<br />\r\nIf so, does it state that on the certificate?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n**No, it has nothing to do with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/search?ie=UTF8&amp;keywords=Mavis%20beacon&amp;tag=successbooks00&amp;index=software&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325" target="_blank">Mavis Beacon</a>&nbsp;other than we suggest it is&nbsp;<br />\r\ngreat typing software and recommend it. .&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ian</p>\r\n\r\n<p>============================================</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Q)I have just finished two certification typing tests.&nbsp; I printed two of them, which is required for an appointment I have.&nbsp; This appointment says minimun required wpm of 45, which I met but &quot;after&quot; errors, the certificate says uncorrected.&nbsp; Does this mean this certificate would not be valid for what I am needing?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-diane white</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(A)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Relax, it has been corrected, all that matters is the NET score, you typed at 55WPM which is very good.&nbsp;<br />\r\nYou can tell any employer to email me about you certificate and we can verify your score. Or even show them this email if needed.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSee copy of certificate attached.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cheers Ian</p>\r\n\r\n<p>=================</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You&rsquo;re awesome!&nbsp; I tried to leave a positive comment on your website, but did not find a customer testimonial section.<br />\r\nThanks so much!<br />\r\n--Tracie S</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks Tracie, glad we could help ; )<br />\r\nCheers Ian</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n======================================</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Is this recognized in Canada? If you are saying it is, and I don&#39;t get recognition from the Police department or government offices, then do you reimburse my fee? Do I need them to sign something saying it is not valid in Canada to get a reimbursement? Thank you, Michelle<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hi Michele,&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you get the self print option and it is not accepted we refund. They don&#39;t have to sign anything we just need details of who&nbsp;<br />\r\ndid not accept it. However, better to ask them as Police often do not accept unsupervised tests.&nbsp;<br />\r\nAlso, sometimes if you show them this,&nbsp; they may accept ours but not others.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee&nbsp;<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/ArticleView.asp?ArticleID=1" target="_blank">Standard No.2708/2001</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>===================================</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder="0" height="60" name="google_ads_frame" scrolling="no" src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-0087522306513536&amp;dt=1162356894625&amp;lmt=1162356894&amp;alternate_ad_url=http%3A%2F%2Funiversityoflife.com%2Fbannerpage.htm&amp;format=468x60_as&amp;output=html&amp;channel=0972599258&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.typingcertification.com%2Fadmin%2FContent1.asp%3FPage%3DFAQs&amp;u_h=864&amp;u_w=1152&amp;u_ah=834&amp;u_aw=1152&amp;u_cd=32&amp;u_tz=330&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_java=true" width="468"></iframe></p>'),
(5, NULL, 'Privacy Policy', 'Yes', '<p>We do not and will not, sell, loan or otherwise share your login, user (or any private info) details with any outside party. Only http://www.typingcertificates.com/ will use your details for any reason and then only to track you as a user and the occasional email update that refers to this or our related sites only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(6, 'Contact Us', 'Contact Us', 'Yes', '<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" style="width:95%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>If you have a suggestion or comment&nbsp;<a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/contact-form.php"><strong>click here</strong></a>&nbsp;for an email form</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>If you are experiencing technical difficulties with:</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Printing certificates</li>\r\n				<li>Test displays</li>\r\n				<li>Timeouts</li>\r\n				<li>Or other problems</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.typingcertification.com/contact-form.php">Click here</a>&nbsp;for a technical reporting form.<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			Best method of contact is via reporting form above, just click on link and we will usually get back to you within 12 hours.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Australian Office</p>\r\n			<br />\r\n			Australian ABN\r\n			<p>56475388353</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;1 Marlock Place<br />\r\n			Woodlands 6018<br />\r\n			Australia</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>USA&nbsp;Office</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Ian Hewitt<br />\r\n			#1963<br />\r\n			1321 Upland Drive,&nbsp;<br />\r\n			Houston, TX 77043<br />\r\n			USA<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>');
